snippet: In rating dozens of spots, there was no consensus in the polls, surveys and analyses of data from social media that poured in this year.
abstract: Stuart Elliott Advertising observes in rating dozens of spots aired during Super Bowl XLVI, there was no consensus in the polls, surveys and analyses of data from social media that poured in; notes viewers and computer users gave their highest and lowest marks to a couple dozen commercials.
lead_paragraph: In rating dozens of spots, there was no consensus in the polls, surveys and analyses of data from social media that poured in this year.
